snippet.textDisplay: Prophet Muhammad (ﷺ) said, “Allah has ninety-nine names, i.e. one-hundred minus one, and whoever knows them will go to Paradise.” Abu Huraira reported Allah's Messenger (ﷺ) as saying: There are ninety-nine names of Allah; he who commits them to memory would get into Paradise.
snippet.textOriginal: Prophet Muhammad (ﷺ) said, “Allah has ninety-nine names, i.e. one-hundred minus one, and whoever knows them will go to Paradise.” Abu Huraira reported Allah's Messenger (ﷺ) as saying: There are ninety-nine names of Allah; he who commits them to memory would get into Paradise.

snippet.textDisplay: Alhamdulilah, after 5 weeks, I memorised all 99 names. I came back here and now, I understood every single word of it compared to my first time watching this. It isn't difficult to remember all 99 names - be consistent and patient in learning. Insha'Allah you'll find it easy too. 😇
